Show HN: I made a site that lets you easily find the best indie startups
text:
Hello hackers,

I made this site to organize the amazing indie startups built by hackers like you. I got overwhelmed by all this cool products so made it easy to search and find startups. I know the list is not big but I am adding more as you are reading this.

I cannot know every startup, so if your startup is not on the list just DM on twitter.

Also Feedback is welcomed!
